12 An Act relating to building codes; directing the
Department of Human Services to work with the State
13 Fire Marshal to develop certain guidelines; providing
that certain child care homes shall not be denied a
14 license; prohibiting stricter requirements; providing
for codification; and providing an effective date.
15
16
