18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1000.31 of Title 59, unless
21 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 The Department of Human Services shall work with the State Fire
23 Marshal to develop guidelines that allow family child care homes and
24 large child care homes to operate under the fire protection
