BOLD FACE denotes Committee Amendments.
1 requ irements of the International Fire Code. Family child care
2 homes and large child care homes shall not be denied a license to
3 operate should they comply with the requirements of the
4 International Fire Code. No agency, municipality, county, or other
5 political subdivision of this state shall place stricter fire
6 requirements than those outlined in the International Fire Code on
7 family child care homes and large child care homes.
8 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
